#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:1
msgid "PyRepl 代码执行"
msgstr "PyRepl Code Execution"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:3
msgid ""
"SimpleLLMFunc 提供内置的 PyRepl 支持，允许 LLM 在一个连续上下文中执行 Python "
"代码。与传统的一次性代码执行不同，PyRepl 保持变量和状态，让 LLM 可以分步执行复杂任务。"
msgstr ""
"SimpleLLMFunc includes built-in PyRepl support, allowing LLMs to execute "
"Python code in a continuous context. Unlike one-shot code execution, PyRepl "
"preserves variables and state so the LLM can solve complex tasks step by "
"step."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:5
msgid "功能特性"
msgstr "Features"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:7
msgid ""
"**IPython subprocess backend**：每个 `PyRepl` 实例对应一个独立子进程，内部运行 `IPython "
"InteractiveShell`"
msgstr ""
"**IPython subprocess backend**: Each `PyRepl` instance corresponds to an "
"independent child process, which internally runs `IPython InteractiveShell`"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:8
msgid "**连续上下文**：变量在多次调用间持久化，LLM 可以分步执行任务"
msgstr ""
"**Continuous context**: Variables persist across calls, enabling step-by-"
"step execution"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:9
msgid "**实时 Streaming**：通过 `event_emitter` 实时获取 stdout/stderr 输出"
msgstr ""
"**Real-time streaming**: Receive stdout/stderr in real time via "
"`event_emitter`"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:10
msgid "**异步不阻塞**：代码执行在独立线程运行，不阻塞主事件循环（适合 TUI/流式 UI）"
msgstr ""
"**Async and non-blocking**: Code runs in a dedicated thread and does not "
"block the main event loop (suitable for TUI/streaming UIs)"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:11
msgid "**Session 隔离**：不同的 PyRepl 实例相互独立，互不影响"
msgstr ""
"**Session isolation**: Different PyRepl instances are independent and do not"
" interfere"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:12
msgid "**完整工具集**：提供 execute_code、reset_repl、list_variables 等工具"
msgstr ""
"**Complete toolset**: Provides `execute_code`, `reset_repl`, "
"`list_variables`, and more"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:13
msgid ""
"**超时保护**：单次 `execute_code` 默认 600 秒活动执行超时；等待 `input()` "
"不计时，且每次收到输入后会重置超时窗口；单次 `input()` 默认 300 秒空闲超时。也可在每次调用时通过 `timeout_seconds` "
"单独覆盖"
msgstr ""
"**Timeout protection**: Single `execute_code` defaults to 600 seconds active"
" execution timeout; waiting for `input()` is not counted, and the timeout "
"window resets after each input is received; single `input()` defaults to 300"
" seconds idle timeout. Can also be separately overridden via "
"`timeout_seconds` in each call."

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:14
msgid ""
"**Runtime primitives**: expose controlled self-reference APIs through "
"`runtime.selfref.history.*` and `runtime.selfref.fork.*`"
msgstr ""
"**Runtime primitives**: expose controlled self-reference APIs through "
"`runtime.selfref.history.*` and `runtime.selfref.fork.*`"

#: ../../source/pyrepl.md:15
msgid ""
"**Origin-aware event stream**: each `EventYield` carries `origin` metadata "
"for stable main/fork routing in TUI or custom UIs"
msgstr ""
"**Origin-aware event stream**: each `EventYield` carries `origin` metadata "
"for stable main/fork routing in TUI or custom UIs"

